The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The use of delay margin and gain margin, two robustness indicators from control theory, suggests that the paper may also belong to the robotics and control subfield. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which suggests that it may belong to the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or neural networks (cs.NE).
